  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Story mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120 levels to unlock and progress. Follow the story of Sophie who is taking over her deceased grandmother Celeste's cheese shop. Customers arrive with cheese party orders, complete matches to fill the orders to get coins and progress through the 12 chapters. Help Cheese Party come back to life, meet the local socialite of a seaside town as you progress through the levels. If story isn't for you use the skip button to get to the cheese.   <br>Smoke cheese, inoculate with mould (blue cheese), freeze and unfreeze are some of the debuffs you can encounter.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finish  puzzles  leaving no cheese  on the board to win.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/653806e9d82d644492389756fbd60a5a.poster.avif?t=1772895948\" aria-label=\"Cheese being moved to match one by one.\" width=436 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/653806e9d82d644492389756fbd60a5a.webm?t=1772895948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/653806e9d82d644492389756fbd60a5a.mp4?t=1772895948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on fun levels without interruption. Complete the level to move on to the next and loop endlessly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/91e69b2bacff48f30cdb6b42f78cada8.poster.avif?t=1772895948\" aria-label=\"Level after level of cheese matching.\" width=438 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/91e69b2bacff48f30cdb6b42f78cada8.webm?t=1772895948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/91e69b2bacff48f30cdb6b42f78cada8.mp4?t=1772895948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Power ups</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move cheese; diagonally, skip cheese, move cheese. Power ups are rewarded randomly for 3 star scores.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Casual play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax. No pay to win or micro transactions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Raincode is a game dev family made up of self taught artists and  developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/0e2f7b48a8e6bba19cb8daf7869b9e15.poster.avif?t=1772895948\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=620 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920060/extras/0e2f7b48a8e6bba19cb8daf7869b9e15.webm?t=1772895948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
